Author: RUMEREO
Title: [ANN] REO coin
Body: This project is a project to innovate the real estate business system of the world by combining Blockchain technology and artificial intelligence (AI). In this project, we will establish the platforms which do not require the existing fees by enabling the individuals to buy and sell the global real estate. Furthermore, we will regard the asset management based on the price expectation using the artificial intelligence as one of the main business.
